ecard Period Processing',31,'lbo','Given the date selected from the create timecard popup -\r\n\r\n<br><br>1. Call Data Interface to check if time card exists on the selected date.<br><br>2. If time card exists, do not proceed; otherwise, go to next step.<br><br>\r\n3. Call Period Interface to determine the timecard period for selected date.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n4. Call Setup Interface to get the set of setupOtions spanning the timecard period determined above. Truncate (if needed) this time card period to get the range of dates (spanning selected date) with consistent setup option assignment to be included in a single new time card.<br><br>5. Check against setup options for current date to see if user is allowed to create timecard for the time card dates.<br><br>6. If user is allowed to create timecard, launch Time Card Entry flow with the following parameters:<br>* TimecardId = null<br>* TimecardStartDate / TimecardEndDate<br>* SetupOptions = Setup Options Queried earlier<br><br>',NULL,'2011-06-07 00:48:57','2011-06-09 02:39:43',0),(108,'Timecard Entry: Basic Page Structure',31,'lbo','The flows and page fragment involved in the time card entry page and basic layout components.',NULL,'2011-06-07 00:52:20','2011-06-07 00:57:03',0),(110,'Timecard Entry: Personal Information: Contextual Action',31,'lbo','This supposedly comes for free from the HR personal information region.<br>',NULL,'2011-06-07 02:17:43','2011-06-09 02:56:25',0),(111,'Timecard Entry: Matrix: Comments',31,'lbo','If user has selected to have stand alone comments entry:\r\n\r\n* comments icon column\r\n\r\n* comments popup',NULL,'2011-06-07 02:23:46','2011-06-07 02:24:35',0),(112,'Timecard Entry: Timecard Header: Status',31,'lbo','Use either read only EO or VO from statuses, or the Summary VO from data. TBD.<br>',NULL,'2011-06-07 02:27:11','2011-06-09 02:55:07',0),(113,'Configuration Interface:  Get Attributes for Layout',30,'lbo','Get the list of all attributes associated with the given layout - with layout