ed on the user input system will run a query to the tables \r\nand display the Consumer Sets information in search results grid.</p>',NULL,'2011-06-08 07:29:32','2011-06-08 07:50:59',0),(124,'Advanced Search',8,'lbo','<p>Lets the user execute advanced queries based on logical operators and wild-cards.</p>Search can be executed using the following parameters<br>Time Consumer Name : Name of the Consumer Set, Choice list of consumers<br>Time Category Name : smart choice-list of all time categories, with a default of \"All Time Entry\".<br>Validation on Save : Yes/No choice-list <br>Time Required : Yes/No choice-list <br>Approval Period : Choice list of all repeating time periods<br>',NULL,'2011-06-08 07:29:41','2011-06-08 07:53:45',0),(125,'Search Page: Action - Create ',8,'lbo','\'Create\' action or \'Create\' button from the Search Results grid are used to create new time consumer set. \r\n                ',NULL,'2011-06-08 07:30:09','2011-06-08 08:14:17',0),(126,'Search Page: Action - Select and Edit',8,'lbo','Only the name and description of a consumer set can be edited, the other\r\n fields will be grayed out in read only mode to protect the consumer set\r\n when it is in use.          \r\n                ',NULL,'2011-06-08 07:30:22','2011-06-08 08:14:31',0),(127,'Search Results',8,'lbo','<p>Results of basic/advanced search </p>                   \r\n                        <p>Generated basic/advanced search results will \r\nbe displayed in this table, it contains Time Consumer Set Name and \r\nDescription of the Consumer Sets.</p>\r\n                       <p> Results table also displays seed data.</p>',NULL,'2011-06-08 07:30:37','2011-06-08 07:54:21',0),(128,'Search Page: Action - Delete',8,'lbo','Can delete time consumer sets if it is not assigned to an employee via Time and Labor Setup Options or attached to a time-card.\r\n',NULL,'2011-06-08 07:30:55','2011-06-08 08:15:08',0),(129,'Capture Name, Description',8,'lbo','\r\n         \r\n                 <p>Time 