),(27,28,'Questionnaire','2011-06-02 05:19:09','2011-06-02 05:19:09',NULL,'Fetch questions and answer sets from database. One is able to handle the dependency relationship between questions. Collect answers and store into the database.'),(28,28,'Task List','2011-06-02 05:19:09','2011-06-02 05:19:09',NULL,'Generate the task list based upon the answers to the questionnaire.'),(29,30,'Timecard Layout Set','2011-06-02 05:19:09','2011-06-02 05:19:09',NULL,'Set of layout configurations. Example: Individual Project Layout Set Configuration, which contains time entry layout, review layout, view layout, template layout, etc., and the attributes are project based.'),(30,30,'Timecard Layout Field','2011-06-02 05:19:09','2011-06-02 05:19:09',NULL,'Set of Layout Fields. Define layout fields base on a time attribute field, or sevearl time attibute fields. There can be dependncy between layout fields. Example: Project, Hours Type.'),(31,31,'Timecard','2011-06-02 05:19:09','2011-06-09 20:59:47',1,NULL),(32,31,'Manager Directs Timecards','2011-06-02 05:19:09','2011-06-02 05:19:09',NULL,NULL),(33,31,'Manager Timecards','2011-06-02 05:19:09','2011-06-02 05:19:09',NULL,NULL),(34,31,'Worker Recent Timecards','2011-06-02 05:19:09','2011-06-02 05:19:09',NULL,NULL),(35,31,'Gantt','2011-06-02 05:19:09','2011-06-02 05:19:09',NULL,NULL),(36,38,'Person','2011-06-02 05:19:09','2011-06-02 05:19:09',NULL,NULL),(37,39,'Project','2011-06-02 05:19:09','2011-06-02 05:19:09',NULL,NULL);
