cm/hcm/time_and_labor/_Layout_Fields/pages/login.htm?url=http://uiprototypes.oraclecorp.com/hcm/hcm/time_and_labor/_Layout_Fields/pages/Manage_Layout_Fields.htm','2011-06-10 03:45:35','2011-06-10 03:45:35',1,'not_mapped','1'),(53,36,'UC2 - Confirm / Use Projects seeded Timecard Fields-copy','Thomas is starting the process of defining a timecard layout set.  Thomas is aware there are delivered layouts, but he wants to define one on his own.\r\n\r\nThe delivered (seeded) layouts are delivered for a Projects User, Payroll User and for both a Projects / Payroll User.  The delivered layout sets contain delivered Timecard Fields, based on the consumming applications default configuration.\r\n\r\nWhile Thomas will build a company defined Layout Set, he decides he\'ll start with the delivered Timecard Fields, since he\'s unsure of what restrictions / modifications to place on the Timecard Fields. \r\n\r\nUI:\r\nhttp://uiprototypes.oraclecorp.com/hcm/hcm/time_and_labor/_Layout_Fields/pages/login.htm?url=http://uiprototypes.oraclecorp.com/hcm/hcm/time_and_labor/_Layout_Fields/pages/Manage_Layout_Fields.htm','2011-06-10 21:01:09','2011-06-10 21:01:34',1,'not_mapped','1'),(54,21,'a path','dsds','2011-06-10 21:50:18','2011-06-10 21:50:18',1,'not_mapped','1');
