 page for Repeating Time Periods which\\n contain the following fields:\\n\\n\\\n  Basic Search\\n\\n\\\n  o     Name - User name for private template\\n\\n\\\n  Advanced Search\\n\\n\\\n  o     Name - User name for private template\\n\\n\\\n  o     Status - Inactive or Active\\n\\n\\\n  o     Operator - this field is coupled with both the Name field, to\\n allow more flexibility to search\\n\\n\\\n  The options for the operator values are: \\n\\n\\\n  o     Greater than\\n\\n\\\n  o     Equals\\n\\n\\\n  o     Does Not Equal\\n\\n\\\n  o     Less Than\\n\\n\\\n  o     Greater Than\\n\\n\\\n  o     Between\\n\\n\\\n  o     Not Between\\n\\n\\\n  o     Is Blank\\n\\n\\\n  o     Is Not Blank\\n\\n\\\n  Also allow for wildcard search in each field.\\n\\\n  Search Results Section\\n\\n\\\n  o     Search Results Grid : displays the user created private templates,\\n and also provides actions which can be applied to private templates.\\n  The columns listed in the search results are the following:\\n\\n\\\n  o     Name - User name for private template\\n\\n\\\n  o     Status - Inactive or Active\\n\\n\\\n  o     Total Hours- Total number of hours for created template\\n\\n\\\n  There will not be seeded private templates, since these are specific\\n to the user..\\n\\\n  Actions for Manage Templates\\n\\n\\\n  o     Create Template\\n\\n\\\n  When using the \\\"create\\\" action or \\\"create\\\" button from the Search\\n Results grid, a user will be able to create a new private template\\n\\n\\\n  o     Edit Template\\n\\n\\\n  When user selects the \\\"edit\\\" action or \\\"edit\\\" button from the Search\\n Results grid, a user will be able to edit an existing private template.\\n\\n\\\n  o     Delete Template\\n\\n\\\n  When user selects the \\\"delete\\\" action or \\\"delete\\\" button from the\\n Search Results grid, a user will be able to delete an existing private\\n template.\\n\\n\\\n  o     Download Template\\n\\n\\\n  When user selects the \\\"Download Template\\\" menu action or \\\"Download\\n template\\\" toolbar button from the Search Results grid, a user will\\n be able to export the template and related choice list values to\\n an excel spreadsheet via ADFdi integration.  See Section 2.3.7 for\\n more information on the ADFdi flow to support disconnected or offline\\n entry mode.  </pre>\\n      \"\niteration_id: 1\n','2011-05-26 20:35:30'),(6540,'Feature',1397,'update','3','--- \nscope: \"2.0\"\nname: Manage Templates - jf\ncreated_at: 2011-04-13 22:38:24 Z\nupdated_at: 2011-05-26 20:35:30 Z\npriority: Must Have\nid: 1397\nfeature_type: \"\"\nfunctional_work_unit_id: 30\ndescription: \"This page facilitates Time and Labor workers managing their own pre-populated timecard templates which can be applied for future\\r\\n\\\n  timecard entry use.  They can search, create, view or delete or export templates from the search/search results page.\\r\\n        \\r\\n\\\n  These are the search fields for finding a private template:\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  o     Basic/Advanced Search page for Repeating Time Periods which contain the following fields:\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  Basic Search\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  o     Name - User name for private template\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  Advanced Search\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  o     Name - User name for private template\\r\\n\\\n  o     Status - Inactive or Active\\r\\n\\\n  o     Operator - this field is coupled with both the Name field, to allow more flexibility to search\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  The options for the operator values are: \\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  o     Greater than\\r\\n\\\n  o     Equals\\r\\n\\\n  o     Does Not Equal\\r\\n\\\n  o     Less Than\\r\\n\\\n  o     Greater Than\\r\\n\\\n  o     Between\\r\\n\\\n  o     Not Between\\r\\n\\\n  o     Is Blank\\r\\n\\\n  o     Is Not Blank\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  Also allow for wildcard search in each field.\\r\\n\\\n  Search Results Section\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  o     Search Results Grid : displays the user created private templates, and also provides actions which can be applied to private templates. \\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  The columns listed in the search results are the following:\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  o     Name - User name for private template\\r\\n\\\n  o     Status - Inactive or Active\\r\\n\\\n  o     Total Hours- Total number of hours for created template\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  There will not be seeded private templates, since these are specific to the user..\\r\\n\\\n  Actions for Manage Templates\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  o     Create Template\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  When using the \\\"create\\\" action or \\\"create\\\" button from the Search\\r\\n Results grid, a user will be able to create a new private template\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  o     Edit Template\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  When user selects the \\\"edit\\\" action or \\\"edit\\\" button from the Search\\r\\n Results grid, a user will be able to edit an existing private template.\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  o     Delete Template\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  When user selects the \\\"delete\\\" action or \\\"delete\\\" button from the\\r\\n Search Results grid, a user will be able to delete an existing private\\r\\n template.\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  o     Download Template\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  When user selects the \\\"Download Template\\\" menu action or \\\"Download\\r\\n template\\\" toolbar button from the Search Results grid, a user will\\r\\n be able to export the template and related choice list values to\\r\\n an excel spreadsheet via ADFdi integration.  See Section 2.3.7 for\\r\\n more information on the ADFdi flow to support disconnected or offline\\r\\n entry mode.  </pre>\\r\\n      \"\niteration_id: 1\n','2011-05-26 20:36:06'),(6541,'Feature',1505,'update','3','--- \nscope: \nname: Search Features\ncreated_at: 2011-05-26 20:33:52 Z\nupdated_at: 2011-05-26 20:33:52 Z\npriority: Must Have\nid: 1505\nfeature_type: \nfunctional_work_unit_id: 172\ndescription: \niteration_id: 1\n','2011-05-26 20:36:13'),(6542,'Feature',1505,'updat