ay\ncreated_at: 2011-05-26 20:21:41 Z\nupdated_at: 2011-05-26 20:36:38 Z\npriority: Must Have\nid: 1501\nfeature_type: UI\nfunctional_work_unit_id: 172\ndescription: |\n  \r\n  \r\n\niteration_id: 1\n','2011-05-26 20:37:44');
