: 2011-04-13 22:38:23 Z\nupdated_at: 2011-05-05 19:18:35 Z\npriority: Should Have\nid: 1349\nfeature_type: \nfunctional_work_unit_id: 143\ndescription: \"Should Have Justification: Allow for the ability to not display certain time entries in the timecard matrix or totals which should not be seen by the worker.\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  By using an  \\xE2\\x80\\x9Cadministrator-only entry\\xE2\\x80\\x9D flag in Group Time Entry, the user can denote which entries are made by the timekeeper or manager.  This will allow filtering of time entries based on who made the entries, if not all entries should be displayed in the timecard to the worker.   These entries would also need to be excluded from timecard totals for the worker as well.\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n      \"\niteration_id: 1\n','2011-05-30 22:07:00'),(6844,'Feature',1349,'update','3','--- \nscope: \"2.0\"\nname: Allow for Suppressing Time Entries by Role - jf\ncreated_at: 2011-04-13 22:38:23 Z\nupdated_at: 2011-05-30 22:07:00 Z\npriority: Should Have\nid: 1349\nfeature_type: Business Rule\nfunctional_work_unit_id: 143\ndescription: \"Should Have Justification: Allow for the ability to not display certain time entries in the timecard matrix or totals which should not be seen by the worker.\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n\\\n  By using an  \\xE2\\x80\\x9Cadministrator-only entry\\xE2\\x80\\x9D flag in Group Time Entry, the user can denote which entries are made by the timekeeper or manager.  This will allow filtering of time entries based on who made the entries, if not all entries should be displayed in the timecard to the worker.   These entries would also need to be excluded from timecard totals for the worker as well.\\r\\n\\\n  \\r\\n      \"\niteration_id: 1\n','2011-05-30 22:07:23'),(6845,'Feature',1351,'update','3','--- \nscope: \"2.0\"\nname: Total Scheduled Hours for Timecard Period - jf\ncreated_at: 2011-04-13 22:38:23 Z\nupdated_at: 2011-05-05 19:20:30 Z\npriority: Should Have\nid: 1351\nfeature_type: \nfunctional_work_unit_